video.title: Kirsten Dunst at the Hounddog movie premiere in NYC
video.description: Actress Kirsten Dunst had no love for the waiting photographers following her attendance to the New York City premiere of "Hounddog", which stars talented young actress Dakota Fanning. Kirsten left out the side door with her head down and a joker smile on her face, telling a fan who asked for a photo with her that she "already did photos on the way in."
